NPC_3: Ah, there you are dad! I was panicked when I saw you weren't home. I apologize. I hope he wasn't too much trouble?
Player: "Not at all. I enjoyed the little treasure hunt we had for the book. Please enjoy and you're welcome to come back once
you are finished."
NPC_3: Thank you so much. I'll try and accompany him next time.
NPC_2: Good evening, stay safe you hear? Here, a charm for good luck.
